<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Winand von Steeg, Pfarrer zu Bacharach</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die freundschaftliche Nachricht des Adressaten und sichert ihm seine Unterstützung zu.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_420" id="209r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wynand<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Steg <expan>Ler<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geıſtlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l3">rechten <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu Bachrach </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l4"><expan>Wırdıg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> doctor / <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> vns nehſt geſandt / Darinn Jr ſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l5">dankbeͣr ſeyt vnd vns ſo <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> dankt <expan>mang<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l7">vnd guts / dıe <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey 
<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l6">vnd von </ab></add> vns <expan>beſchehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / vnd wıe Jr eẅch ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıenſt hinfür als begırlıch vnd wıllıklıch erpıett etc . Haben </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l9">wır wol vnd gern <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . Vnd danken des <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l10">fleıſʒ / Vnd wo wir <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>wırdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> . <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> dıenſt vnd guten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l11"><expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> . das <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır auch mıt <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l12"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omin</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_420" id="209r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wynand<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Steg, <expan>ler<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geistlich<ex>er</ex></expan> rechten, <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu Bachrach</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Wirdig<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>l<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> doctor, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> uns nehst gesandt, darinn ir so dankbeͣr seyt
                        und uns so <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> dankt
                            <expan>mang<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>, <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und
                        guts, die <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey <add>und von</add> uns
                                <expan>beschehe<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn, und wie ir ewch zu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dienst hinfür als begirlich und
                        williklich erpiett etc., haben wir wol und gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>, und danken des
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz. Und wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>, dienst und guten
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir auch
                        mit <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> tun. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omin</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
